I MEAN, THIS EARLY,

00:37:55,073 --> 00:37:57,776
THERE SHOULD BE SUCH
A PASSIONATE RESPONSE TO YOU,

00:37:57,776 --> 00:38:01,079
SUCH A PASSIONATE RESPONSE TO
