HOW YOU SEE THE FUTURE,

00:38:08,787 --> 00:38:10,155
I THINK THERE'S A DISCONNECT,

00:38:10,155 --> 00:38:12,357
AND SO, FOR THOSE REASONS,
I'M OUT.

00:38:12,357 --> 00:38:14,058
OKAY. I APPRECIATE IT.

00:38:17,195 --> 00:38:18,496
BEAUTIFUL DESIGNS.

00:38:18,496 --> 00:38:21,432
I DON'T SEE IT TODAY
AT THAT VALUE.

00:38:21,432 --> 00:38:22,967
I'M OUT.

00:38:22,967 --> 00:38:25,336
OKAY. APPRECIATE IT.

00:38:25,336 --> 00:38:28,239
UM...

00:38:28,239 --> 00:38:30,074
O'Leary: I THINK
