00:38:30,074 --> 00:38:31,976
I THINK YOU MADE
THE ASSUMPTION

00:38:31,976 --> 00:38:34,913
THAT JUST 'CAUSE SOMEONE ELSE
OUTSIDE OF SHARK TANK

00:38:34,913 --> 00:38:38,116
WOULD PAY YOU A RIDICULOUS
