00:38:44,455 --> 00:38:47,158
AN MBA IS NOT A PREREQUISITE
FOR SUCCESS AT ALL.

00:38:47,158 --> 00:38:48,526
I HAVE ONE, TOO.
UNDERSTOOD.

00:38:48,526 --> 00:38:49,727
WHO CARES?

00:38:49,727 --> 00:38:51,996
YOU HAVE TO GO MAKE MONEY
FOR INVESTORS.

00:38:51,996 --> 00:38:53,531
THAT'S ALL THAT MATTERS.

00:38:53,531 --> 00:38:57,135
I PERSONALLY THINK IT'S WORTH
ABOUT 1.5 MILLION BUCKS.

00:38:58,369 --> 00:39:01,606
AND IF I WAS GONNA
GIVE YOU $500,000,

00:39:01,606 --> 00:39:03,708
