00:39:03,708 --> 00:39:06,311
I MEAN, I THINK,
MAYBE...50/50.

00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:09,647
NO, I'M SERIOUS.

00:39:09,647 --> 00:39:11,950
I'M SERIOUS, TOO.
NO. NOT HAPPENING.

00:39:11,950 --> 00:39:14,118
[ CHUCKLES ]

